    <title>mac安装mysql以及问题</title>
    <url>/2020/04/19/installMysqlForLocal/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>*由于我使用mac，所以本文基于mac讲述搭建过程</p>
<h2 id="1-官方下载地址"><a href="#1-官方下载地址" class="headerlink" title="1.官方下载地址"></a>1.官方下载地址</h2><p><a href="https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/mysql/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/mysql/</a><br><a id="more"></a></p>
<h2 id="2-步骤"><a href="#2-步骤" class="headerlink" title="2.步骤"></a>2.步骤</h2><p>1.1 下载完成后，双击直接安装，按照步骤走，在最后会提示输入八位密码<br>1.2 安装完成后，点击系统偏好设置，选择MySQL<br><img src="//sundragonsk.com/2020/04/19/installMysqlForLocal/mysqlSetting.png" alt="setting"><br>1.3 可以看到数据库的活动实例，配置等信息，启动数据库服务（可选择随电脑启动，默认已勾选）</p>
<ul>
<li>注意有可能在按下start键后出现如下错误:<br><font color="red">Warring the /usr/local/mysql/data directory is not owned by the ‘mysql’ or ‘_mysql’ user &lt;/&gt;<br>这应该是某种情况下导致/usr/local/mysql/data的宿主发生了改变。<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo chown -R mysql /usr/local/mysql/data</span><br><span class="line">或者</span><br><span class="line">sudo chown -R  _mysql:wheel  /usr/local/mysql/data</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">参数说明：</span><br><span class="line">-c 显示更改的部分的信息</span><br><span class="line">-f 忽略错误信息</span><br><span class="line">-h 修复符号链接</span><br><span class="line">-R 处理指定目录以及其子目录下的所有文件</span><br><span class="line">-v 显示详细的处理信息</span><br><span class="line">``` g</span><br><span class="line">1.4 以上mysql已经装好，想在终端直接使用mysql 指令，还需配置路径，打开.bash_profile 文件，添加PATH=$PATH:/usr/local/mysql/bin，步骤如下</span><br><span class="line">```&#123;bash&#125;</span><br><span class="line">cd /usr/local/mysql/bin4</span><br><span class="line">vim ~/.bash_profile</span><br><span class="line">添加内容：</span><br><span class="line">  PATH=$PATH:/usr/local/mysql/bin</span><br><span class="line">想要配置的内容立即生效：</span><br><span class="line">  source ~/.bash_profile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></font></li>
</ul>
]]></content>
